text: Coney Island is a 1943 American musical movie directed by Walter Lang and starring Betty Grable, George Montgomery, Cesar Romero, Charles Winninger, Phil Silvers, Frank Orth. It was nominated for Academy Award in 1944 and was remade in 1950 as Wabash Avenue. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1943 musical movies Category:1940s American musical movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Walter Lang
